name: Leftover Chili Colorado tostadas with face melting Carolina Reaper sauce
description: This is a picture of food. Specifically, a meal that was prepared from leftovers found in the freezer. It’s good to have food in the freezer. However, there are millions that don’t know what that feels like. When you collect this digital representation of food, mangiamaniacal will donate $1 to The Hunger Project.  The original art was destroyed… and it was delicious.
